Package: artclaude
Title: Anthropic Claude Toolkit
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Bobby", "Fatemi", , "bobby@artalytics.app", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Experimental R interface to Anthropic's Claude API with full support
